1.0.2.name: wordpress/wp-social-seo-booster
1.0.2.description:
WP Social SEO Booster adds Facebook Open Graph, Twitter Card and Google Rich Snippets (Microdata / schema.org) to your site to boost your sites search engine visibility. It is the only plugin which does include ALL the different types of microdata which are supported by Google.

Special Offer for the Pro Version (only valid until August 31, 2013) We celebrate the 50,000+ downloads and offer you a 50% discount for the Pro version, but only until August 31, 2013. Use the following coupon code to get the discount: booster50 here

Features of this plugin include:

  • Adds all the proper meta tags from existin content. No need to manually setup anything.
  • Works with any SEO Plugin, such as WordPress SEO by Yoas
